data.enText: in which three or more groups, nations, etc. take part

data.chText: 有多条边的；有多个部分的

example.ex: Many want to abandon the multilateral trade talks in Geneva.
example.tran: 很多国家想退出在日内瓦举行的多边贸易会谈。

value.def: Multilateral means involving at least three different groups of people or nations.
